history.content:
Dear 2020 Computer Science Graduates,

Congratulations on your pending graduation!  We are excited to provide you with the opportunity to celebrate your many accomplishments at Cal. As such, we are planning an online Celebration of 2020 L&S Computer Science graduates. This celebration will be available remotely to you, your family and friends, and the college community. Each graduate will have the opportunity to be recognized with an official slide that can be personalized with your photo, and which can be downloaded and shared on social media.

Students who wish to participate will need to register for the celebration. I will send a follow up message with details about the online celebration and registration by the end of this week. At this time we do not have an in-person event scheduled, but should that become an option in the future we will work hard to communicate that information to you.  Thank you all for your patience and understanding. 

Sincerely,

Antoine Davis
history.subject: L&S Computer Science Online Celebration for CS Graduates
